Class Order

java.lang.Object
main.Menu
main.Order
Direct Known Subclasses:
Customer
public class Order
extends Menu
Order Class is responsible for taking the customer's food, quantity, and price choices. Uses the inherited foodInMenu array from the Menu Class.
